videos.description: Evina Westbrook makes a 3-pointer from the top of the key to extend Tennessee's lead in the third quarter.
videos.headline: Westbrook reaches 15 points with 3-pointer

videos.description: Mercedes Russell almost gets the ball stripped but stays with it to make the bucket.
videos.headline: Russell makes tough bucket for Lady Vols

videos.description: Tennessee intercepts an inbound pass made by Texas to prevent a Texas basket late in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Lady Vols create turnover to secure lead

videos.description: Lady Vol head coach Holly Warlick says her team showed toughness down the stretch which was key in No. 11 Tennessee's 82-75 win against No. 2 Texas.
videos.headline: Warlick proud of her team for upsetting No. 2 Texas
